window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A sexy, emotional, suspenseful romance novel from number one </b><b><i>New York Times </i></b><b>best-selling author Lauren Blakely with all new narration from Zachary Webber and Ava Erickson!</b></p> <p>Some women are just off-limits.</p> <p>But that doesn’t stop me from wanting Elle Mariano. She’s clever, big-hearted, and the sexiest woman I’ve ever met.</p> <p>The thing is, she’s fighting the demons of her past, and do I ever know how hard those are to battle.</p> <p>So I try my best to be her shoulder to lean on. Until the night we combust. And one night turns into hot, dirty days, and secret trysts.</p> <p>If it all sounds too good to be true, it is. Because once I learn the secret she’s keeping from me, my entire family’s future turns riskier than I ever imagined.</p> <p>Especially since the bastards who tried to tear my family apart years ago are tailing both of us now. Our every move...</p> <p>Additional voices from Tim Paige, Scott Brick, Shane East, Maxine Mitchell, Samantha Cook, Brian Pallino, Jason Clarke, and more!</p>"; 
